Sublime Text 3.2.2 Build 3211 key licence
Make sure you edit the host files mentioned below
linux or macOs : /etc/hosts
Windows : C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc

Append this 4 lines at the end of file.
#Sublime Text 3
127.0.0.1 license.sublimehq.com
127.0.0.1 45.55.255.55
127.0.0.1 45.55.41.223

Note: If you don't have permissions to edit above file
copy the host file to your home directory
append those lines and after saving replace it with original one using admin privileges
